# LumiCode â€“ Code-Activated LED Robot

## Description
**LumiCode** is an educational robot that lights up LEDs based on code inputs. It helps beginners learn programming and electronics through hands-on robotics.

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- LED Strips  
- Python / Arduino IDE  

## Key Features
- Interactive LED patterns  
- Coding-based control  
- Educational and fun  

## My Role
Programmed LED sequences, designed circuits, and created tutorials for learning.


